title: [Twisted Trail]
description: The mountain juts out here, forcing a detour to the southwest.  As you look up the mountainside, you notice a building nestled back on a cliff.  It seems to be intact, if dilapidated, and although the detail is lost at this distance, it seems to be some sort of abbey.
